      "message": "Initially, I did have these exact expressions in place of the 202 and 204 -- that didn't work, but I don't remember the details (they may have evaluated to 0, due to being uninitialized). I would have preferred this to the hard-wired constants, but I thought leaving the expressions could be useful.\n\nI have noticed that Sonar complains about some comments being code that really weren't, and the common denominator seemed to be the existence of the ';'. So, I got rid of the ';' here, in hopes that Sonar would back off.",
